trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientReferenceCollection" /> contains a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference" /> with the specified URL; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
